<template>
    <el-container>
        <el-header>
            <el-row>
                <el-col>员工管理系统</el-col>
            </el-row>
        </el-header>

        <el-main>
            <el-form ref="form" :model="staff" :rules="rules">
                <el-form-item label="账号：" prop="account">
                    <el-col :span="4">
                        <el-input type="text" v-model="staff.account"></el-input>
                    </el-col>
                </el-form-item>
                <el-form-item label="密码：" prop="password">
                    <el-col :span="4">
                        <el-input type="password" v-model="staff.password"></el-input>
                    </el-col>
                </el-form-item>
                <el-form-item>
                    <el-button native-type="submit" type="primary" :span="4">登录</el-button>
                    <el-button native-type="reset" type="warning" :span="4">重置</el-button>
                </el-form-item>
            </el-form>
        </el-main>
        <el-footer>

        </el-footer>
    </el-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: "Login",
    data() {
        return {
            staff:{
                account: '',
                password: '',
            },
            rules:{
                account:[

                ],
                password:[

                ],
            }
        }
    },
}

</script>
